  &lt;tr&gt;
    &lt;td&gt;462&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;td&gt;Testall target fails in server/test to invalid MAXSCALE_HOME path specification&lt;/td&gt;
  &lt;/tr&gt;
  &lt;tr&gt;
    &lt;td&gt;467&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;td&gt;max_slave_replication lag is not effective after session creation&lt;/td&gt;
