  &lt;tr&gt;
    &lt;td&gt;468&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;td&gt;query_classifier : if parsing fails, parse tree and thread context are freed but used&lt;/td&gt;
  &lt;/tr&gt;
  &lt;tr&gt;
    &lt;td&gt;469&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;td&gt;rwsplit counts every connection twice in master - connection counts leak&lt;/td&gt;
  &lt;/tr&gt;
